<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en" lang="en" xml:fb="http://www.facebook.com/2008/fbml">
<head>
	<title>Mitoo is down for maintenance</title>
	
	<style>
	html {background-color:#e1e1e1; font-family: arial}
	.container{
		width: 500px;
		margin: 100px auto;
		background-color: white;
		padding: 30px;
		border: 1px solid #CCC;
		box-shadow: 1px 1px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}
	.container h1 {
		text-align:center;
		color: #333;
		font-size: 35px;
		font-weight:normal;
		margin-bottom: 10px;
	}
	.container p {
		text-align: center;
		color: #666;
	}
	</style>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="//use.typekit.com/tsk1uqu.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript">try{Typekit.load();}catch(e){}</script>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="container content">		
		<h1>Mitoo is down for maintenance</h1>
		<% if(@reason.nil? && @dealine.nil?) %>
		<p>We're busy updating the site and will be back shortly.</p>
		<% else %>
		<p>We're <%=@reason%> and will be <b>back <%=@deadline%></b>.</p>
		<% end %>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
